HEADWORD: Exoculate
<hw>Ex*oc"u*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exoculatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>exoculare</ets> to exoculate;
<ets>ex</ets> out + <ets>oculus</ets> an eye.]</ety> <def>To deprive of
